        "action": "Raise the threshold for postgraduate loan repayments in line with inflation",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Raise the threshold at which postgraduate loans are paid back for the first time since they were established. They are still at \u00a321,000, a level below the minimum wage for a full time worker, and have never been upgraded to reflect inflation.",
